'''反強暴安全套'''（Anti-rape device），是一種阻止[[強姦|強姦]]的裝置，第一個類似的裝置是15世紀時期的[[貞操帶|貞操帶]]。雖然反強暴安全套發明的目的是為了阻止強姦，但是批評者認為應該是懲罰強姦犯來阻止強姦，而不是將防止強姦的責任交給受害者。

==统计数据==
一部分著名的反強暴安全套是在[[南非|南非]]这个强奸案发生率高<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://theconversation.com/rape-in-south-africa-why-the-system-is-failing-women-54924|title = Rape in South Africa: why the system is failing women|last = |first = |date = February 18, 2016|website = The Conversation|publisher = |access-date = March 8, 2016|archive-date = 2018-10-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181014172817/http://theconversation.com/rape-in-south-africa-why-the-system-is-failing-women-54924|dead-url = no}}</ref>、定罪成功率低<ref>{{Cite journal|last = Langa-Mlambo|first = Lerato|date = July 22, 2012|title = Violence Against Women In South Africa|url = http://vaw.sagepub.com.libezp.lib.lsu.edu/content/18/5/580.full|journal = Obstetrics & Gynaecology Forum|access-date = March 14, 2016|archive-date = 2020-03-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200314010559/https://login.libezp.lib.lsu.edu/login?qurl=http%3A%2F%2Fvaw.sagepub.com%2Fcontent%2F18%2F5%2F580.full|dead-url = no}}</ref>的国家创造出来的。南非活动家表示，当地的法律体系在预防或减少强奸和其他针对妇女的暴力行为方面没有起效。

根据[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]2001年的一项研究，全世界20％的妇女一生中遭受过至少一次的强奸或强奸未遂的经历。<ref>{{Cite journal|last = Fayard|first = Nicole|date = April 1, 2011|title = Moi Quand On Dit Qu'une Femme Ment, Eh Bien, Elle Ment'1: The Administration Of Rape In Twenty-First Century France And England & Wales.|url = http://eds.a.ebscohost.com.libezp.lib.lsu.edu/eds/pdfviewer/pdfviewer?vid=33&sid=fce7d1ee-9f37-45b0-a015-3dd27a74b045%40sessionmgr4001&hid=4105|journal = French Politics, Culture & Society|access-date = March 14, 2016|archive-date = 2020-03-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200314010541/https://login.libezp.lib.lsu.edu/login?qurl=http%3A%2F%2Feds.a.ebscohost.com%2Feds%2Fpdfviewer%2Fpdfviewer%3Fvid%3D33&sid=fce7d1ee-9f37-45b0-a015-3dd27a74b045%40sessionmgr4001&hid=4105|dead-url = no}}</ref>

